    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use this power as a swift action when you fail a Bluff, Diplomacy, or Intimidate check outside of combat. You suffer no negative effects due to the failed check, and the next round you can attempt the check again without the usual penalty for a failed attempt. You can use this ability once per day, and one additional time per day for every 4 levels beyond 1st.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Copycat power of the Trickery Domain.</p>"
